! Title: Remove Discord Annoyances
! Expires: 28 days
! Homepage: https://github.com/Katzenwerfer/uBlock-Filter-Lists/blob/master/RemoveDiscordAnnoyances
! Description: Remove some annoying items from the Discord interface

!!Remove Super Reaction buttons
discord.com##div[aria-label="Add Super Reaction"]
discord.com##button[id="super-reaction-picker-tab"]
discord.com##div[id="message-add-reaction-1"]

!!Remove Super Reactions from messages
discord.com##div[aria-label*="Super reacted"]
discord.com##div[aria-label*="super reaction"]:upward(1)
discord.com##div[aria-label*="super reactions"]:upward(1)
